== Overview ==
The Plasma IDT is the second class of bot-equippable Plasma Shield projector. The design combines three standard [[Plasma (Shield)|Plasma Shield]] units into a combined unit that allows for an enhanced overlapping shield layer.

== Where to Acquire ==
The Plasma IDT can be bought in the workshop after acquiring [[Plasma Technology]].
